    "For the case of one charge carrier in the ferromagnetic background, we discuss the expected absence of thermalization in Sec.",
    "III C. In Sec.",
    "IV, we increase the number of electrons but keep the fully polarized spin background.",
    "Section V covers a different initial state in a large many-body subspace, for a single charge carrier.",
    "Finally, we present our conclusions in Sec."
